OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FPersistent
OL,6,Frain will spread from the west this
OL,7,Fevening, occasionally heavy. Drier and
OL,8,Fclearer weather following on
OL,9,Fovernight. Fresh southerly winds this
OL,10,Fevening, strong along the east coast.
OL,11,
OL,12,CMonday:FDry with some sunshine in the
OL,13,Fmorning. Clouding over in the
OL,14,Fafternoon with some showery rain
OL,15,Fspreading to the west.
OL,16,
OL,17,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:
OL,18,FTuesday and Wednesday begin frosty but
OL,19,Fstay dry and sunny. Early rain on
OL,20,FThursday then bright with the odd
OL,21,Fshower.
